- You asked-we listened! Introducing Premium and Elite Subscription and much more with this release!
- Premium Subscription: Includes 1 free boost/month, Unlimited Rewinds (for accidental passes), 100 Super Likes/Month (5/day), Unlimited 'Likes' (no limit/day), and an ad-free experience!
- Elite Subscription: Includes all Premium features, plus the ability to see who's liked you for an instant match!
- New features: 'Super Likes', 'Boosts' and 'Rewind' features
- 'Super Likes': Increase your chances of a match by sending a Super Like and letting them know you're super interested! (1 free/day!)
- 'Boosts': Boost your profile to be one of the first profiles seen in your area!
- 'Rewinds': Unlimited Rewinds for accidental passes with both Premium and Elite subscription
